---
title: Lemon Pepper Pork with Roast Veggies & Creamy Pesto Dressing
description: It's meat and three veg, but not as you know it. Let us show you how a few small steps can totally reinvent an everyday meal. Simply toss the roast veggies with tangy balsamic vinegar and top off your lemon pepper pork with creamy pesto. And there you have it folks, meat and three veg that will not disappoint.
